        public Palette(java.lang.String id,
               java.awt.Color backgroundColor1,

               java.awt.Color backgroundColor2,
               java.awt.Color foregroundColor2,
               java.awt.Color backgroundColor3,
               java.awt.Color foregroundColor3)
        Instantiates a palette with all its mandatory colours
        Parameters:
        id - menuName (identifier) of the palette (used to get it from the map)
        backgroundColor1 - global background color of all non-button elements (also the background color of a clicked button)
        foregroundColor1 - global foreground (font) color of all non-button elements
        backgroundColor2 - background color of a button when it is selected (but not clicked yet)
        foregroundColor2 - foreground (font) color of a button when it is selected (and/or clicked)
        backgroundColor3 - background color of a button when it is unselected (and not clicked)
        foregroundColor3 - foreground (font) color of a button when it is unselected (and not clicked)
